---
title: Cheesy BBQ Baked Beans with Crusty Garlic Bread
description: These baked beans really live up to their name, both with their time in the oven where all the flavours mix and mingle into a cosy taste sensation, and with the gooey cheese topping that turns these beans into a hearty feast.
